  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206340/extras/b3ec52dadda885cf5e70221287fa6345.poster.avif?t=1724439926\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206340/extras/b3ec52dadda885cf5e70221287fa6345.webm?t=1724439926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206340/extras/b3ec52dadda885cf5e70221287fa6345.mp4?t=1724439926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aokana - EXTRA2 is the official Misaki after story for Aokana.<br><br>Aokana is a Japanese-style visual novel produced by sprite, a Japanese developer of romance VNs.<br>It won numerous awards in the year of its release in Japan for its art, music, and characters.</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206340/extras/457f8f29877f3efa1cdd54c6cac3f82f.avif?t=1724439926\" width=600 height=151 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206340/extras/7530feca1d8c087d4fe33b2cf2611ff3.avif?t=1724439926\" width=600 height=246 /></span><br><br><br><strong><u>Story:</u></strong><br>It's been a few months since Misaki won the fall Flying Circus tournament, and summer is coming to a close. <br>Those feelings of triumph are fading, with new questions rising in their place. <br>How far does Misaki want to take FC, and how will she deal with her new-found fame? <br>Her relationship with Masaya is going from strength to strength, but how will she make good on her promise to help him make it? <br><br>Join this power couple as they face off challengers from all directions while trying to make the ultimate decision: just what fu